{"tid":1260511,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"熱狗知道，抗爭沒有用","createTime":"2019-06-27T00:43:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T14:30:56.000Z","uid":389,"like":20,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ced5d2d9ec11f7bd020814718366e4851302bf","tid":1260511,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:43:50.000Z","msg":"所以留響屋企打飛機捉鬼<br />\n叫人衝係鬼<br />\n叫人守係鬼<br />\n無比人拉係鬼<br />\n比人拉重唔係鬼<br />\n未坐監係鬼<br />\n坐緊監係鬼<br />\n放監係鬼<br />\n走得慢係鬼<br />\n走得快係鬼<br />\n<br />\n只有蟲太唔係鬼<br />\n陳雲係神（發神經個神）<br />\n過氣毓民唔係人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/59ayd3j.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F59ayd3j.png&h=3fb9d9a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Rh1nWF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Rh1nWF.png&h=9fd54919&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgVm7om.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgVm7om.png&h=a1028cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/45Ufsoo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F45Ufsoo.png&h=0bd99acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一邊話人食人血饅頭<br />\n一邊玩自己龜頭<br />\n一邊屌人地食饅頭<br />\n一邊自己食熱血月餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RA6hFJp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRA6hFJp.png&h=eb1670af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱狗必須死，捉到要用黎煮熱狗肉煲<br />\n熱狗唔係狗，連狗都不如"},{"pid":"d92645359f03c53e7b1559935f1358eb578f8841","tid":1260511,"uid":25999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T00:53:27.000Z","msg":"推比啲兒登仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7690a7531268f6270da46477b0ee15f394d5d1fa","tid":1260511,"uid":31215,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"有冇必要呢啲時候翻舊史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尋日無理抹黑梁頌恆<br />\n今日狙擊鄭松泰<br />\n唔好呢個時候做呢啲黨派紛爭"},{"pid":